/ S3 Public Access Setting Changed Detection
/ Detects when public access settings on S3 buckets are modified
/ Risk: Misconfiguration exposing sensitive data to the public internet
/ MITRE ATT&CK: Defense Evasion (TA0005)
/ Recommended: Alert immediately, verify if change was authorized and revert if not

index=* sourcetype="aws:cloudtrail" eventName="PutBucketPublicAccessBlock"
| table eventTime, userIdentity.userName, requestParameters
| sort - eventTime
